OL,7,FDamning reports have revealed the
OL,8,Fextent of bullying, harassment,
OL,9,Fsexism, and nepotism in two of Wales'
OL,10,Ftroubled fire services following an
OL,11,FITV Wales investigation into their
OL,12,Fworkplace culture.
OL,14,FIt comes as a jointly commissioned
OL,15,Findependent culture review of the
OL,16,FNorth Wales and Mid and West Wales
OL,17,FFire and Rescue Services was published
OL,18,Fon Wednesday.
