OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FMid and West Wales fire service was
OL,8,Fbranded an "operational boys club",
OL,9,Fwith staff and former staff describing
OL,10,Fthat personal connections with senior
OL,11,Fleaders "fostered favouritism and
OL,12,Fnepotism."
OL,14,FNearly half (47%) of people who
OL,15,Fresponded to the survey reported
OL,16,Fpersonal experiences with bullying and
OL,17,Fharassment in the service since June
OL,18,F2021, and over half (54%) had
OL,19,Fwitnessed such behaviours, the report
OL,20,Ffound.
